  <text>
    <body resp="#CM">
      <div type="letter">
        <div corresp="#surface-1">
          <opener>
            <dateline>
              <placeName ref="#VSCG">Quarto, Villa Spinola</placeName>
              <lb/><lb/>
              <date xml:id="d4" when="1862-03-13">March 13, 1862</date>
              <lb/><lb/>
            </dateline>
            <salute>
              Esteemed Mr. <persName ref="#GRI">Giovanni Grillenzoni</persName>,
              <placeName ref="#REG">Reggio</placeName>
            </salute>
            <lb/><lb/>
          </opener>

          <p>
            In accordance with the agreements made
            <lb/>
            with the board in charge of the <choice><sic>Institution</sic><corr>Foundation</corr></choice>
            <lb/>
            of <seg xml:id="tiro-comment1" ana="#tiro">Target Shooting</seg>, I hereby authorize you to take action
            <lb/>
            for the establishment, in that patriotic
            <lb/>
            city, of a shooting range, and to coordinate,
            <lb/>
            as necessary, with the local authorities.
          </p>

          <p>
            Warmly encourage
            <lb/>
            the inhabitants of Reggio, in my name,
            <lb/>
            to diligently pursue the
            <lb/>
            foundation of shooting ranges in each municipality
            <lb/>
            of the province. Let them gather
            <lb/>
            in a provincial society; let the wealthier citizens
            <lb/>
            offer the initial expenses as a gift to the Fatherland.
            <lb/>
            I place great trust in the active
            <lb/>
            patriotism of the city of <placeName ref="#REG">Reggio</placeName>.
          </p>

          <closer>
            <salute>Yours,</salute>
            <signed><persName ref="#GAR">G. Garibaldi</persName></signed>
            <p xml:id="stamp-placeholder"/>
          </closer>
        </div>

        <div corresp="#surface-2">
          [see physical note]
        </div>
        <div corresp="#surface-3">
          <p>[physical marks]</p>
        </div>
